    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "0a36a362-57e6-4200-b619-b6b441126d41",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "Inheritance &amp; Bootstraps",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN",
        "PublicId": "103584802551",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_octopus.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 68a957ea-36c3-4233-bdbd-c892bd032e05).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47,\rYour next targets are two Italian pensioners who built up a smaller fortune during the boom of the economy before neoliberalism failed and annihilated the middle class.\rThe problem is is that in their ignorance, they do not share any of that with their son to help him start his life, and believe that he should just &quot;pull himself up by his bootstraps&quot; as they did, not taking into account the changed materialistic factors.\rSo the son has hired us to speed up the inheritance process.",
